   156	
   157	```text
   158	reference/compose/
   159	├── README.md                 # How to bring it up + what each service does + ops notes
   160	├── compose.yaml              # The Compose file. Three services + three volumes.
   161	├── .env.example              # Default env values; gitignored ".env" is the real file.
   162	└── healthcheck/
   163	    └── smoke.sh              # Bash script: bring up, wait for healthy, assert volume,
   164	                              # tear down. Used by both the human verification step
   165	                              # and the new compose-smoke CI job.
   166	
   167	.github/workflows/ci.yml      # New job: compose-smoke
   168	.gitignore                    # Add: reference/compose/.env
   169	docs/roadmap.md               # Mark 10a complete
   170	reference/README.md           # Update Compose row from "Phase 10" → "Phase 10 chunk 10a"
   171	AGENTS.md                     # Append Phase 10 chunk 10a paragraph
   172	```
   173	
   174	**Not** created in 10a:
   175	
   176	- Any Dockerfile under `reference/services/*/` — those land in 10b.
   177	- Any `PostgresStore` code in `reference/packages/eden-storage/` —
   178	  defers until 10b ships the consumer.
   179	- `reference/packages/eden-blob/*.py` — defers to 10d.
